divs: Sighting DetailsI was vacationing all around Arizona in 2009. We stopped to camp at a secluded place called Ashurst Lake, where I began taking pictures. I didn't see these in the sky when I was snapping pictures, but saw them when I brought my camera home to view photos on my computer. The image is exactly as it was taken, nothing was done to the photograph.
